---
layout: base.liquid
title: 最新消息
---
<header>
  <h1>Decap CMS 示範站（11ty 版）</h1>
  <p>build-time 產生純 HTML · 每篇文章有獨立頁面 · SEO 友善</p>
  <a class="admin-link" href="/admin/">✏️ 進入內容後台</a>
</header>

<main>
  <div class="grid">
    {%- assign posts = collections.news | reverse -%}
    {% for post in posts %}
      <a class="card" href="{{ post.url }}">
        {% if post.data.thumbnail != "" %}<img src="{{ post.data.thumbnail }}" alt="">{% endif %}
        <div class="body">
          <time>{{ post.data.date | date: "%Y-%m-%d" }}</time>
          <h3>{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
          <p>{{ post.data.summary }}</p>
        </div>
      </a>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</main>
